<HEADER>
A7530 &Cx1f; tie-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CIRCUITS-BUDGET-NYT &LR;      06-16 0336
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CIRCUITS-BUDGET-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Circuits stories from The N.Y. Times News Service for Thursday,
June 17:
</P>
<P>
   CIR-DESKTOP-DESIGN (Undated) _ New designs for PCs, inspired by
the iMac and fueled by the development of flat screens, could spell
the end of the beige box. By Michel Mariott.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-MP3 (Undated) _ MP3 and other web music formats explained.
By David Kushner.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   With
</P>
<P>
   CIR-MP3-COPYRIGHT (Undated) _ Sidebar on copyright law.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-MP3-HOWTO (Undated) _ Sidebar on how to make, get and play
MP3.
</P>
<P>
   With graphic.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-MP3-TECH (Undated) _ Short on how it works.
</P>
