   CIR-COMPUTER-COLUMN (Undated) _ The weekly computer column:
Review of a new ultralight thinkpad. By Peter H. Lewis.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-GEEK-NOTES (Undated) _ Techno news and notes: Apple
quicktime, new turn in worm defense, all digital recorder, and
communal web surfing.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-HELLO-KITTY-GAME (Undated) _ Hello Kitty Game for the Sony
Playstation. By J.C. Herz.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-SLIDE-RULES (Undated) _ Slide-rule aficionados on the Web.
By Ian Austen.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-WEB-MICROSCOPE (Undated) _ Students do science with internet
connection to electron microscope. By Louise Yarnall.
</P>
<P>
