</P>
<P>
   BOOK-TALK (Undated) _ The weekly books column. By Martin Arnold.
</P>
<P>
   GIRLS-BOOK-REVIEW (Undated) _ ``The Girls' Guide to Hunting and
Fishing,'' by Melissa Bank (Viking). Reviewed by Christopher
Lehmann-Haupt.
</P>
