``fatigue'' with Clinton affecting Gore, the vice president's
strategists moved up the announcement to begin distancing Gore from
Clinton.
</P>
<P>
   From Carthage, Gore traveled to Iowa, the scene of the first
presidential balloting next year. He also will visit New Hampshire,
New York, California and Washington before returning to the
nation's capital.
</P>
