<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-16 20:19 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8247 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-VIOLENCE17-COX     06-16 0752
