<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-POPE-NYT, which moved in ``i''
news file.) 
c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``It's easy to sing, but it's not easy to do.''
</P>
<P>
   _POPE JOHN PAUL II, 79, after young people in his hometown gave
him a traditional greeting, ``May You Live 100 Years.''
</P>
