At the Red Blazer in Manhattan, Cary Hoffman, a lifelong fan of
Frank Sinatra, is getting a chance to sing in his idol's style with
the Stan Rubin orchestra. Hoffman, who is approaching 60, has been
a commercial jingle writer, a talent manager and a comedy club
owner. (Chang W. Lee/New York Times Photo)
